&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
[ckan.controllers.api] Validation error: "{'&lt;span class="underline"&gt;type': 'Validation Error', '&lt;/span&gt;junk': [u'The input field &lt;span class="underline"&gt;junk was not expected.']}"
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
